sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS (service-ca)
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MRBFF as model-registry-ui BFF<br/>8043/TCP TLS (service-ca)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS
    participant MRService as Model Registry Service<br/>HTTPS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Accessing Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuth: Reencrypt TLS<br/>HTTPS/8443, service-ca cert
    Note over OAuth: Validates OAuth cookie/token<br/>Checks projects:list permission
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080 (localhost)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
    Backend-->>OAuth: Static React SPA assets
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>Browser: Dashboard UI

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1 (cont): K8s API Pass-through

    Browser->>Router: API Request /api/k8s/*<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>Cookie auth
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/6443<br/>Bearer Token (user's token)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s API Response
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS
    Router-->>Browser: API Response

    Note over Browser,MRService: Flow 2: Model Registry UI (Module Federation)

    Browser->>Router: GET /model-registry/api/*<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>Cookie auth
    OAuth->>MRBFF: HTTPS/8043<br/>x-forwarded-access-token<br/>TLS (service-ca)
    MRBFF->>MRService: HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token<br/>TLS
    MRService-->>MRBFF: Registry Data
    MRBFF-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS
    Router-->>Browser: Model Registry Data

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query

    Browser->>Router: GET /api/prometheus/*<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>Cookie auth
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>Thanos: PromQL Query<br/>HTTPS/9092, TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (SA token)
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metrics Data
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS
    Router-->>Browser: Metrics Data

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: WebSocket: K8s Watch Stream

    Browser->>Router: Upgrade /wss/k8s/*<br/>WSS/443
    Router->>OAuth: WSS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: WS/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch Stream<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch Events (streaming)
    Backend-->>OAuth: WS Events
    OAuth-->>Router: WSS Events
    Router-->>Browser: Real-time Updates
